        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f5",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "The fake invoices used by the petitioner were recorded in the legal books and reflected in the relevant period declarations.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 812,
        "end_char": 937,
        "text_hash": "85fa4d7fbc43c265",
        "display_location": "0:5",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": "Başvurucu tarafından kullanılan bu faturaların yasal defterlere kaydının yapıldığı ve ilgili dönem beyannamelerine intikal ettirildiği hususlarının tespit edildiği gerekçesiyle"
      },
      "fact_type": "material",
      "actor_source": "petitioner",
      "date": null,
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
      "provenance": {
        "extraction_method": "llm",
        "model_id": "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning",
        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f6",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "A tax inspection report dated 21 November 2014 was prepared.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 938,
        "end_char": 1021,
        "text_hash": "a75fa24202a86cf4",
        "display_location": "0",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": " 21/11/2014 tarihli vergi inceleme raporu düzenlenmiştir."
      },
      "fact_type": "material",
      "actor_source": "petitioner",
      "date": "2014-11-21",
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
      "provenance": {
        "extraction_method": "llm",
        "model_id": "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning",
        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f7",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "In the report, by reducing the VAT carryover from 2009, tax loss penalty VAT was assessed for the March 2010 period.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 1024,
        "end_char": 1175,
        "text_hash": "ad9d193a3cfc7fab",
        "display_location": "0",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": "Anılan raporda 2009 yılından devreden katma değer vergisinin azaltılması suretiyle 2010 yılı Mart dönemine ilişkin olarak vergi ziyaı cezalı katma değer vergisi tarhiyatı yapılmıştır."
      },
      "fact_type": "material",
      "actor_source": "petitioner",
      "date": null,
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
      "provenance": {
        "extraction_method": "llm",
        "model_id": "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning",
        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f8",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "The petitioner filed a lawsuit in Istanbul Tax Court seeking annulment of the assessed tax loss penalty VAT for March 2010.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 1178,
        "end_char": 1314,
        "text_hash": "b146919c2b80aab9",
        "display_location": "0:7",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": "Başvurucu 2010 yılı Mart dönemine ilişkin olarak tarh edilen vergi ziyaı cezalı katma değer vergisinin iptali istemiyle İstanbul  Vergi Mahkemesinde (Mahkeme) dava açmıştır."
      },
      "fact_type": "procedural",
      "actor_source": "petitioner",
      "date": null,
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
      "provenance": {
        "extraction_method": "llm",
        "model_id": "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning",
        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f9",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "Istanbul Tax Court rejected the petitioner's lawsuit with its decision dated 15 May 2015.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 1317,
        "end_char": 1387,
        "text_hash": "f7c1d1470ef015e1",
        "display_location": "0",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": " Mahkeme, başvurucunun açmış olduğu davayı 15/5/2015 tarihli kararı ile reddetmiştir."
      },
      "fact_type": "procedural",
      "actor_source": "lower_court",
      "date": "2015-05-15",
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
      "provenance": {
        "extraction_method": "llm",
        "model_id": "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning",
        "prompt_id": null,
        "run_id": null,
        "temperature": 0.1,
        "timestamp": "2026-02-17T21:36:57.023378"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f10",
      "type": "fact",
      "text": "In other lawsuits against assessments based on the 21/11/2014 tax inspection report concerning the petitioner company, the lawsuits were rejected.",
      "anchor": {
        "doc_id": "sha256:affcd09b708d",
        "start_char": 1550,
        "end_char": 1710,
        "text_hash": "d7bb3b38b3bd58d6",
        "display_location": "0:9",
        "secondary_spans": [],
        "surface_text": "başvurucu Şirket hakkında tanzim edilen 21/11/2014 tarihli vergi inceleme raporu uyarınca yapılan tarhiyatlara karşı açılan diğer davalarda davanın reddine karar verildiğinden"
      },
      "fact_type": "material",
      "actor_source": "lower_court",
      "date": null,
      "date_approximate": false,
      "disputed_by": null,
      "court_finding": "accepted",
      "confidence": "high",
